&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Summary:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role consists in optimisation of daily power procurement processes and support in identifying, securing power procurement contracts for the development of Bitfury’s data centers in Norway/Sweden and Canada.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Duties and responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Permanent review of Company’s current contract prices;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identification of market opportunities and potential new suppliers, execute contract re-negotiations;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define tactics and methods:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and refine electricity purchase tactics;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Refine methids of electricity cost reporting and analysis;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop tactics and methods implementation plan (e.g. propose additional electricity suppliers);&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop hedging policy (electricity and certificates):
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform historical price analysis;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare risk profile assessment and proposal for hedging portfolio content, including time horizons. PPA opportunity mapping;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Developing hedging instructions;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implementing hedging plan.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Daily power procurement (EU, North America)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support with search for new promising sites for future Data Centers with cheap energy and available power.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support with paper work, managing external consultants and/or subcontractors (certified estimates for applications, preliminary design, etc), upon request;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
