&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a motivated macro rates trader to contribute his/her market expertise in trading USD, EUR and GBP securities and derivatives. The associate PM is expected to evaluate market opportunities, generate trade ideas and assist the PM in managing the overall portfolio. He/she must be a strong communicator with the broker-dealer community and is able to actively source relevant information in a timely manner to stimulate discussion among team members.&lt;/p&gt;
