&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2-5 Years of trading experience in US, Europe and UK rates, including bonds and derivatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Complete understanding of macro factors driving interest&amp;nbsp;rate markets, including fundamental economic data, central bank policy actions, and short-term flow dynamics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong foundation in&amp;nbsp;fixed income analytics for&amp;nbsp;bonds, futures, swaps as well as risk analytics&amp;nbsp;and PnL components&lt;/li&gt;
