&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Opportunity:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;The successful candidate will be critical to the successful development, launch, and maintenance of&lt;br&gt;products and capabilities. This candidate will think big about the future of crypto and how you can bring&lt;br&gt;individual investors and institutions into the crypto economy more quickly. As a key contributor within the&lt;br&gt;Marketing team, you’ll be tasked with developing effective marketing strategies and plans through&lt;br&gt;strategic proven marketing strategies; developing positioning, messaging, competitive differentiation, and&lt;br&gt;enabling the Sales and Marketing teams to ensure they are aligned and work efficiently to generate and&lt;br&gt;close opportunities. Most importantly, as our dedicated marketer you’ll drive results and significantly grow&lt;br&gt;the adoption of Okcoin products and features.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Be Doing:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;● Support Growth through delivery of new products and improve upon GTM strategies for existing&lt;br&gt;products&lt;br&gt;● Execute and track program deliverables, milestones, action items, dependencies, risks, and&lt;br&gt;mitigation plans&lt;br&gt;● Develop solid working relationships with cross-functional teams to best understand and deliver on&lt;br&gt;business goals and priorities.&lt;br&gt;● Track performance of campaigns to provide data-backed insights to optimize campaigns and find&lt;br&gt;new opportunity areas&lt;br&gt;● Prepare presentations and clearly communicate findings from initiatives to management and to&lt;br&gt;the broader organization&lt;br&gt;● Be the voice of the customers and Influence Product Design and Product pipeline to satisfy user&lt;br&gt;needs&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We Look For In You:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;● 3+ years of GTM experience with a track record of managing all aspects of a successful product&lt;br&gt;launch.&lt;br&gt;● Proven in orchestrating a wide range of marketing initiatives - everything from strategic planning -&lt;br&gt;to content marketing - to go-to-market implementation.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;● Excellent written and verbal communications skills; ability to translate strategy into clear&lt;br&gt;actionable plans&lt;br&gt;● Ability to solve complex problems and rapidly formulate a clear point-of-view&lt;br&gt;● Excellent prioritization skills and willingness to roll up one&amp;amp;#39;s sleeves to get the job done&lt;br&gt;● Thrive when working in a collaborative and cross-functional environment and inspire others&lt;br&gt;around you&lt;br&gt;● Solid analytical, problem-solving, and decision-making skills&lt;br&gt;● Experience with Wordpress, Hubspot, Google Analytics&lt;br&gt;● BA/BS degree; preferably in marketing&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to Haves:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;● You either are already or are eager to become an expert in the blockchain and cryptocurrency&lt;br&gt;landscape and will understand how speculators, traders, digital asset exchanges, blockchain&lt;br&gt;money services businesses and financial institutions operate.&lt;br&gt;● Experience working in a disruptive technology, successfully launching products, ideally, within&lt;br&gt;FinTech, eCommerce, SaaS, AdTech, or Digital Wallet business experience&lt;br&gt;● A history (and preference) of being both strategic, analytical and execution-oriented&lt;br&gt;● MBA preferred, but not required&lt;br&gt;● Experience working with teams across offices and time zones.&lt;/p&gt;
